    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>broccoli </strong>into small florets</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>broccoli florets</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of your <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until beginning to char</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> in<strong> </strong>150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for an initial 5-6 min, stirring frequently, or until starting to brown</p><p>Add your<strong> linguine </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel lengths off your<strong> courgette[s]</strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of <strong>courgette ribbons</strong>, stack into a pile and fold in half lengthways, then finely slice \u2013 this is your <strong>courgetti</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>courgetti</strong> to a colander</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked linguine</strong> over the <strong>courgetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong>, and return to the pot \u2013 this is your<strong> courgetti linguine</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the bacon is starting to brown, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and your <strong>dried oregano</strong> and cook for a further 1-2 min or until cooked through and fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chicken stock </strong>with your <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>cornflour </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until thickened</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is thickening, chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once thickened, remove from heat and stir in <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) until melted</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>drained courgetti linguine </strong>and <strong>charred</strong> <strong>broccoli florets</strong> with a few splashes of <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>and a generous knob of <strong>butter </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the courgetti is slightly softened and mix until creamy \u2013 this is your <strong>bacon alfredo courgetti linguine with broccoli</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/bacon-alfredo-courgetti-linguine-with-broccoli/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>bacon alfredo courgetti linguine with broccoli</strong> topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
